<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1039151" n="1"/> 
  <opener><salute>Viro Juveni Doctissimo <rs key="pers_DE-588-122682769" type="person">Fr. Lud. Spr<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>nglino</rs> Amico meo charissimo</salute>
    <lb/><foreign xml:lang="grc">χαίρειν καὶ εὐπράττειν</foreign><note type="editorial">"chaírein kaì eupráttein" = "Sei gegrüsst und lebe wohl".</note></opener>
<p><lb/>Accepi, charissime, gemella Tua perennantis erga me amoris <del><gap/></del>Tui testimonia, binas nempe Tuas
  <lb/><rs type="lostletter">epistolas</rs> suavissimas, quarum altera <rs key="place_GEO-2988507" type="place">Luteti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>, altera <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> mihi reddita fuit. L<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tus sane intellexi
  <lb/>ex illis felicem Tibi hactenus fuisse itineris successum, gratulor Tibi quod <rs key="place_GEO-2907911" type="place">Heidelberg<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> in tanta licet
  <lb/>Eruditorum penuria nihilominus inveneris aliquos, qui Te ibi retineant, optoque ut omnia Tibi por<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ro, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipue id <del><gap/></del>quod nunc non sine delectamento, ut spero, tractas studium Chaldaicum et Rabbi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nicum, ex animi voto succedant, et absoluto feliciter itinere amplis multijug<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> eruditionis spo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>liis refertus domum redeas. Gaudeo <rs key="pers_DE-588-140736662" type="person">Christium</rs> meum Tibi <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basileam</rs> transeunti aliquid grati pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sta<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re potuisse, et magis adhuc gauderem, si mihimet tum temporis domi esse debitoque erga Te ami<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cum tam charum officio defungi licuisset; sed quod tunc neglectum fuit resarcietur, ut spero, prox<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ima illa, de qua spem facis, conjunctione nostra. Exultavit profecto cor meum, quum ex prio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ribus Tuis <rs type="letter">literis</rs> percepi, nobis Tui cum <rs key="pers_DE-588-1168632560" type="person">Risoldo</rs> nostro suavissimo hic videndi vere proximo copi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>am fore; ah quam impatienter expecto eorum pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentiam, <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> quibus <rs key="place_GEO-2660646" type="place">Genev<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> tam <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>gre divelli
  <lb/>potui? ah quantum mihi excitas vestri desiderium dum dulcissimam illam nostram conversatio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nem <rs key="place_GEO-2660646" type="place">Genevensem</rs> mihi in mentem revocas? imo qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> me rapis plenum amoris Tui, dum imaginem
  <lb/>meam Tibi nunquam non observari nuntias? vel potius, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> raperis Tu, charissimum caput,
  <lb/>cui ad exprimendum affectum erga me Tuum ipsi c<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>lindri, ellipses, Planet<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, vortices <abbr><choice><orig><g ref="#pp">pp.</g></orig><reg>etc.</reg></choice></abbr> inservire
  <lb/>debent? credo Te lectis illis, quos Tibi <rs key="place_GEO-2660646" type="place">Genev<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> reliqueram, <rs key="pers_DE-588-118639056" type="person">Fontenellii</rs> <rs type="biblio">libris</rs>, et in specie lepido
  <lb/>illo <rs type="biblio">de pluralitate mundorum Discursu</rs> tanta affectum fuisse voluptate, ut defixis perpetuo in
  <lb/>sph<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ras, vortices, Planetas et similia cogitationibus somnians h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c effudisse mihi videaris; et sane
  <lb/>jam antea prospiciebam <rs type="biblio">libellos</rs> hosce Tibi nequaquam displicituros esse, oblitusque eram Te hac
  <lb/>de re in pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cedentibus meis <rs type="letter">literis</rs> interrogare; mihi certe admodum placent, multo magis tamen
  <pb facs="1039152" n="2"/> 
  <lb/>eorum <rs key="pers_DE-588-118639056" type="person">Auctor</rs>, cum quo <rs key="place_GEO-2988507" type="place">Parisiis</rs> non semel su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>a cum animi voluptate confabulari mihi licuit. C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>te<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ter hunc fuerunt alii no<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>ulli Viri Clari et Eruditi, non quidem tam magno, ut tu credis,
  <lb/>numero, quorum conversatione vel Occasione <rs type="organisation">Comitiorum Academicorum</rs>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> frequentandi mihi
  <lb/>facultas fuit, vel quia alias Bernoulliani nominis fautores erant, gavisus sum, quique me omni
  <lb/>favorum grnere ita prosecuti sunt, ut me <rs key="place_GEO-2988507" type="place">Luteti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> h<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>emem varias ob causas transigere renuentem
  <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>gre dimiserint. In <rs type="place">Patriam</rs> igitur, Deo sit gratia, feliciter redux, si quid agam quidve mihi ani<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mi sit qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ris, scito me vel otiosum domi latere, vel subinde cum su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>a amicorum meorum, <rs type="person">Chri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>stio</rs> nempe et <rs key="pers_DE-588-1132220874" type="person">Raillardo</rs>, qui haud ita pridem ad nos quoque reversus Te quam maxime salutatum
  <lb/>cupit, tempus t<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>diosum fallere, diemque illam, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Te et <rs key="pers_DE-588-1168632560" type="person">Risoldum</rs> nostrum nobis pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentes sistet,
  <lb/>su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>o cum desiderio expectare. Age igitur, charissime, proposito Tuo itinere feliciter defungere, <rs key="place_GEO-2661552" type="place">Bernamque</rs> delatus valens valentem <rs key="pers_DE-588-1168632560" type="person">Risoldum</rs> Tuum amplectere; </p>
<closer>Age, vale et ama Tuum,
  <lb/>quem amici nomine su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>opere beas, <signed><rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolaum Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs>.</signed> <dateline>Scriptum <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1710-11-12">12. <abbr>Nov.</abbr> 1710</date>.</dateline> <hi rend="u"><rs key="place_GEO-2907911" type="place">Heidelbergam</rs>.</hi></closer>
<postscript>
<p><abbr>P. S.</abbr> Causam dilat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> scriptionis <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-140736662" type="person">Christio</rs> meo cognosces.</p>
</postscript>
</div>
